<item>
            <title>[SOLR-9032] Alias creation fails in new UI</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-9032</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Using the Collections UI to create an alias makes a call like this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://$HOST:8983/solr/admin/collections?_=1461358635047&amp;amp;action=CREATEALIAS&amp;amp;collections=%5Bobject+Object%5D&amp;amp;name=assets&amp;amp;wt=json&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://$HOST:8983/solr/admin/collections?_=1461358635047&amp;amp;action=CREATEALIAS&amp;amp;collections=%5Bobject+Object%5D&amp;amp;name=assets&amp;amp;wt=json&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The collections param is effectively &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;object Object&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; which is clearly wrong, and should be a comma separated list of collections.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
